description:
[h1] Description [/h1]
This is a simple mod  that adds an imprisonment Category and tweaks a few things for various Prison mods to neatly package them together with proper research. (Requires all original mods)

[h1] List of Changes [/h1]
- Added Imprisonment Category to build Menu, put the following into it:
) Crucifix
) Prisoner Pole
) Prisoner pole (Burning)
) Prisoner Cage
- Renamed Burning Prisoner Pole => Prisoner Pole (Burning)
- Modified Research: Imprisonment (Tech Level 3) unlocks:
) Crucifix
) Prisoner Pole
) Prisoner Cage
-New Research: Execution (Requires Imprisonment research) unlocks: -) Prisoner Pole (Burning)

[h1] Required Mods [/h1]
[url=https://steamcommunity.com/workshop/filedetails/?id=1222324217] General Modifications [/url]
[url=https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=1544810522] Burned Alive [/url]
[url=https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=1589668839] Crucifixion [/url]

[b]Make sure to load this Below all required Mods[/b]
